The Talent "Hunting Party" from the Hunter grants 1% Agility bonus per Point in the Talent. It does multiply with other Talent-Agility bonus.
 
The following code is needed after the code for the Survivalist
(Rawr.Hunter.HunterCalculations, line 693 in build 34153)
                // Hunting Party
                talents.BonusAgilityMultiplier = ((1.0f + talents.BonusAgilityMultiplier) * (1.0F + .01f * talentTree.HuntingParty)) - 1.0f;
